OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWinds easing
OL,6,Fto become mainly light inland, but
OL,7,Fstaying breezing along the coast. Low
OL,8,Fcloud is also likely to spill inland,
OL,9,Fhowever some clearer spells remain
OL,10,Flikely across western parts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAny cloud clearing back to the
OL,13,Fcoast through the morning, to give
OL,14,Fgood sunny spells. However feeling a
OL,15,Ftouch cooler, with a light northerly
OL,16,Fbreeze, fresher into north Norfolk
OL,17,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
