OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FFine
OL,6,Fand dry, with plenty of sunny spells
OL,7,Fand likely staying clearer overnight.
OL,8,FCooler than recent days with
OL,9,Ftemperatures easing to nearer normal
OL,10,Ffor mid-July.
